OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780470345
OL,3,CTravel disruption as London
OL,4,CUnderground strike underway
OL,6,FCommuters are facing mass travel
OL,7,Fdisruption in London as the first of
OL,8,Ftwo 24-hour tube strikes begins.
OL,10,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,11,FTransport union (RMT) walked out on
OL,12,FTuesday and will strike again on
OL,13,FThursday after last-ditch talks failed
OL,14,Fto resolve a dispute over the working
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FThe two sides met for five hours on
OL,18,FMonday, with the assistance of the
OL,19,Fconciliation service Acas, but the
OL,20,Ftalks ended without any resolution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
