OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780470345
OL,3,CTravel disruption as London
OL,4,CUnderground strike underway
OL,6,FTube services were affected early on
OL,7,FTuesday as RMT members mounted picket
OL,8,Flines outside stations.
OL,10,FTransport for London (TfL) warned
OL,11,Fpassengers that during the strike
OL,12,Faction there would be no service on
OL,13,Fthe Circle and Waterloo and City
OL,14,Flines. The Piccadilly and Bakerloo
OL,15,Flines are part suspended, and there is
OL,16,Falso no service on the Metropolitan
OL,17,Fline between Baker Street and Aldgate,
OL,18,Fand the Central line between White
OL,19,FCity and Liverpool Street.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
