PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780470345
OL,3,CTravel disruption as London
OL,4,CUnderground strike underway
OL,6,FServices are expected across all other
OL,7,FTube lines on both days, but there
OL,8,Fwill be disruption to journeys and
OL,9,Fservice levels will vary across the
OL,10,FLondon Underground network.
OL,12,FOn both days, there will be a limited
OL,13,Fservice before 6.30am, and customers
OL,14,Fare advised to complete their journeys
OL,15,Fby 9pm.
OL,17,FLondon Underground services are
OL,18,Fexpected to run as normal on Wednesday
OL,19,Fand Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
