PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780470345
OL,3,CTravel disruption as London
OL,4,CUnderground strike underway
OL,6,FThe union opposes a new four-day work
OL,7,Fweek because of the impact on the
OL,8,Flength of shifts and other issues.
OL,10,FAn RMT spokesperson said: "Despite our
OL,11,Fbest efforts in Acas talks, TfL have
OL,12,Ffailed to provide assurances on our
OL,13,Fmembers' deeply held concerns around
OL,14,Ffatigue, reduced flexibility, shift
OL,15,Flengths and the impact these proposals
OL,16,Fcould have in a safety-critical role
OL,17,Flike Tube driving.
OL,19,F"We remain available for meaningful
OL,20,Ftalks, but strike action tomorrow will
OL,21,Fnow go ahead."
