OL,3,CTravel disruption as London
OL,4,CUnderground strike underway
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA TfL spokesperson said: "It is
OL,12,Fbitterly disappointing that despite
OL,13,Ffive hours of meetings with the RMT at
OL,14,FAcas and repeated assurances that the
OL,15,Ffour-day working week proposals will
OL,16,Fremain voluntary, RMT has chosen to
OL,17,Fcontinue with its disruptive strike
OL,18,Faction. We will do all we can to
OL,19,Fprovide as much service as possible
OL,20,Fduring this action."
